title: 11/27/2020 - Hour 1 - Cowboys Blew It When They Paid Zeke
itunes:title: 11/27/2020 - Hour 1 - Cowboys Blew It When They Paid Zeke
description:
On today's episode of The Herd, Doug Gottlieb fills in for Colin. When it comes to MVP candidates, Doug feels we need to pump the brakes a little bit on the Dashaun Watson chatter. These days, Ezekiel Elliott is just an "okay" running back for the Cowboys, not blown away. Pat Forde joins in to talk College football rankings, SEC, BIG 10 and how the eye test is slightly skewed this season.
